title: Liz Cheney Thinks She Is Abraham Lincoln | Daily Best of August 17 | Rick & Bubba
description:
After losing the Wyoming GOP primary in a landslide, Liz Cheney compares herself to Abraham Lincoln. Joe Biden signs the Inflation Reduction Act into law and then forgets where he is and what he's supposed to do with his hands. Bubba and Adler work on plans to see the upcoming historic rocket launch of NASA's SLS. And lastly, since some of us can't reach or even see our toes, we decide we all need to stretch more.
